&lt;h1 id=&#34;mathjax&#34;&gt;MathJax&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://geoffruddock.com/math-typesetting-in-hugo/&#34;&gt;This approach&lt;/a&gt; was used to enable &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mathjax.org/&#34;&gt;MathJax&lt;/a&gt;, with the minor edit that step 2 needed to be applied to the file &amp;ldquo;head.html&amp;rdquo; instead of &amp;ldquo;header.html&amp;rdquo; (this seems to be specific to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/LukasJoswiak/etch&#34;&gt;etch theme&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inline math &lt;code&gt;$E=mc^2$&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
